<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>{{ title }} — Hors Champ 74</title>
<meta name="description" content="{{ title }} — Hors Champ 74, l'info Haute-Savoie sans filtre.">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400;1,700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
:root {
  --noir: #1a1714;
  --encre: #2c2825;
  --terre: #8B3A1A;
  --rouge: #C4522A;
  --creme: #faf7f2;
  --sable: #f5f0e8;
  --gris: #7a736b;
  --gris-clair: #c8c0b4;
  --bordure: #ddd5c8;
  --max: 720px;
}
body {
  background: var(--creme);
  color: var(--encre);
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ── HEADER ── */
header {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  background: var(--creme);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--bordure);
  height: 58px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 0 20px;
}
.h-logo {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.h-logo span {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-weight: 900;
  font-size: 18px;
  color: var(--encre);
}
.h-logo span em { font-style: normal; color: var(--rouge); }
nav { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 28px; }
nav a {
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gris);
  text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s;
}
nav a:hover { color: var(--rouge); }
.nav-btn {
  background: var(--rouge) !important;
  color: white !important;
  padding: 7px 18px;
  border-radius: 2px;
}
.nav-btn:hover { background: var(--terre) !important; }

/* ── ARTICLE ── */
.article-wrap {
  max-width: var(--max);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 120px 24px 80px;
}
.article-meta {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.article-date {
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gris-clair);
}
.article-category {
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border: 1px solid currentColor;
}
.cat-pollution { color: var(--terre); }
.cat-dechets { color: var(--gris); }
.cat-animaux { color: #4a7c59; }
.cat-good-news { color: #C4522A; }
.cat-montagne { color: #2c5f7c; }
.cat-curieux { color: #8b6914; }
.cat-default { color: var(--gris); }

h1.article-title {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 48px);
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.15;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  color: var(--encre);
}

.article-image {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  display: block;
}

.article-body {
  font-size: 17px;
  line-height: 1.75;
  color: var(--encre);
}
.article-body p {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.article-body p:first-of-type {
  font-size: 19px;
  color: var(--noir);
  font-weight: 400;
}

/* ── RETOUR ── */
.back-link {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--rouge);
  text-decoration: none;
  margin-top: 48px;
  padding-top: 24px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--bordure);
  width: 100%;
  transition: gap 0.2s;
}
.back-link:hover { gap: 14px; }

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer {
  background: var(--sable);
  padding: 48px 24px;
  text-align: center;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--bordure);
  margin-top: 64px;
}
footer p {
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gris);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
footer a {
  color: var(--rouge);
  text-decoration: none;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <a href="/" class="h-logo">
    <span>HORS CHAMP <em>74</em></span>
  </a>
  <nav>
    <a href="/fil.html">LE FIL</a>
    <a href="/coupgueule.html">COUP DE GUEULE</a>
    <a href="/" class="nav-btn">SIGNALER →</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<article class="article-wrap">
  <div class="article-meta">
    <span class="article-date">{{ date | dateFR }}</span>
    {% if category %}
      <span class="article-category cat-{{ category }}">{{ category }}</span>
    {% else %}
      <span class="article-category cat-default">Brève</span>
    {% endif %}
  </div>

  <h1 class="article-title">{{ title }}</h1>

  {% if image %}
    <img src="{{ image }}" alt="{{ title }}" class="article-image">
  {% endif %}

  <div class="article-body">
    {{ content | safe }}
  </div>

  <!-- Réactions des lecteurs (Cusdis — modérées avant publication) -->
  <section style="margin-top:56px;padding-top:32px;border-top:1px solid #e5ded2">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:24px;margin-bottom:6px">Réagir</h2>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:#8a8378;margin-bottom:20px">Vous en savez plus ? Vous étiez sur place ? Vous avez vu autre chose ? Complétez l'article ci-dessous — les meilleurs ajouts seront repris. Pas besoin de compte, tout est relu avant publication.
    <div id="cusdis_thread"
      data-host="https://cusdis.com"
      data-app-id="e4e3d434-5dc7-455a-9414-090db3cc2159"
      data-page-id="{{ page.fileSlug }}"
      data-page-url="https://horschamp74.fr{{ page.url }}"
      data-page-title="{{ title }}"
    ></div>
    <script defer src="https://cusdis.com/js/widget/lang/fr.js"></script>
    <script async defer src="https://cusdis.com/js/cusdis.es.js"></script>
  </section>
